name: MessageEvent
description:
An event describing a message sent/received between Spans.

Generated from protobuf message google.devtools.cloudtrace.v2.Span.TimeEvent.MessageEvent

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.description: Type of MessageEvent. Indicates whether the message was sent or received.

params.description: An identifier for the MessageEvent's message that can be used to match SENT and RECEIVED MessageEvents. It is recommended to be unique within a Span.
